15
00:00:54,319 --> 00:00:56,840
that you would never think of until it just happens

16
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,840
and you encounter it and then you just have to

17
00:00:59,020 --> 00:00:59,681
think on your feet.

18
00:01:00,181 --> 00:01:02,761
Unexpected sort of lessons, some of which are

19
00:01:04,222 --> 00:01:08,223
kind of interesting and novel and some of which are horrible and painful.

20
00:01:09,084 --> 00:01:12,045
So everyone here is speaking for themselves.

21
