00:12:06,977 --> 00:12:08,858
Austin, he said I was a cynical guy, so I'm a cynical guy.

202
00:12:09,218 --> 00:12:09,998
Depressed most of the time.

203
00:12:10,739 --> 00:12:12,420
So my talk is like learning to let go, right?

