00:13:03,885 --> 00:13:08,131
So, you know, it's like trying to convince like an Ariana Grande fan to, you know, to like Pantera.

223
00:13:08,491 --> 00:13:09,533
It's just probably not going to happen.

224
00:13:09,973 --> 00:13:15,481
So it's, it's, I guess I learned that, well, I guess, I guess a long time ago,

225
00:13:15,901 --> 00:13:17,684
but it still irks me to this day that I...

226
00:13:18,495 --> 00:13:21,236
people say, Grant, I think it's shit, just do it again.

