00:13:31,839 --> 00:13:32,959
and you've been saving up for ages

234
00:13:33,379 --> 00:13:34,780
for this great steak that you've heard about

235
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:35,540
that you really want to have.

236
00:13:36,020 --> 00:13:36,880
And like, you go to the restaurant,

237
00:13:36,900 --> 00:13:38,021
you sit down, the waiter comes across

238
00:13:38,081 --> 00:13:39,441
and like, he says to you, what are you going to have, sir?

239
00:13:39,901 --> 00:13:41,202
I'm going to have this fantastic steak.

240
00:13:41,342 --> 00:13:42,782
Can't wait for it, I've waited such a long time.

